title: Tia's Mexican and Mediterranean Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Pizza, Mediterranean, Beer/Wine, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Has a separate vegan menu including a daily vegan happy hour 5-7pm; pizzas, enchiladas, and chimichanga burritos all could be made with vegan cheese. Also a gluten-free menu, traditional Mexican cocktails and beers.
